{"tid":1657770,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（又助攻）林奠：批評外國國會肆意介入香港事務","createTime":"2019-10-16T08:43:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T09:39:42.000Z","uid":125168,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9896c69f603e348071f77129c6f2f011acb0c78c","tid":1657770,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T08:43:54.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】林鄭月娥表示，對美國眾議院通過《香港人權與民主法案》感到遺憾，而外國政府制裁香港官員是毫無理據，批評外國國會肆意介入香港事務。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥表示，不需要外國議員會指出香港的人權、自由及司法的重要性，因此這是香港的核心價值。<br />\n<br />\n被問及「光復香港、時代革命」是否一個會被取消參選人資格的口號，林鄭月娥表示，參選人資格需由選舉主任按法律以及按照當時的資料而作決定。"},{"pid":"d012007e045123ed85634ed134f2344d733ede3f","tid":1657770,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T08:44:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MHn4YGm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMHn4YGm.jpg&h=a9bf801a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"73763b12c87b7f140bc0c7bb470d1e9866d72315","tid":1657770,"uid":125168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T08:45:02.000Z","msg":"大家記得一齊通知聲議員，呢個puppet leader又廢up啦"},{"pid":"61f9db98d52daa45a1f4b95429bc8b3612f692ec","tid":1657770,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T08:46:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1cd4fa6568d73b3aa2678050df80b03771c5f80","tid":1657770,"uid":310328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T08:46:33.000Z","msg":"知唔知點解林鄭唔肯回應五大訴求啊？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1657591\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1657591</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bb53b25f806b343900766a18fdc794ce20957532","tid":1657770,"uid":155580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T08:46:56.000Z","msg":"葉劉: 妹妹你可唔可以收聲休息下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da2d64895df3dda638554943d1446cbd0b43232a","tid":1657770,"uid":